{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Hs6Kt3nPKN98Uku8AP7MCB","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Claude (sonnet) — 2026-03-15 19:26:38\n     2→# Duration: 564s — Exit: 0\n     3→# Prompt:\n     4→#   Analyze the title extraction failures below. Read each failing input file\n     5→#   and the current implementation at lib/text-classifier/title-extractor.ts.\n     6→#   \n     7→#   Write your analysis to tools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md explaining:\n     8→#   1. What patterns the algorithm fails on\n     9→#   2. Why each specific failure occurred\n    10→#   3. Common themes across failures\n    11→#   \n    12→#   Do NOT modify any code files. Only write the feedback.md file.\n    13→#   \n    14→#   Failures:\n    15→#   - File: /Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Smażona zielona fasolka.real.txt\n    16→#     Expected: 'Smażona zielona fasolka'\n    17→#     Got: ''\n    18→#   \n    19→#   Results file: tools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/results.txt\n    20→\n    21→============================================================\n    22→\n    23→Written to `tools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md`.\n    24→\n    25→## Summary\n    26→\n    27→The single failure traces to **two interacting bugs** in the trilingual title layout (`Smażona zielona fasolka` / `GREEN BEANS BORKEUM` / `그린빈 볶음`):\n    28→\n    29→**Primary cause — bilingual join contamination:** The bilingual detection correctly removes `\"GREEN BEANS BORKEUM\"` as a standalone candidate, but the filter only suppresses candidates *starting with* the translation text. The 2-line join `\"Smażona zielona fasolka GREEN BEANS BORKEUM\"` and 3-line join including Korean both pass `passesHardFilters` and remain in `scoredForThreshold`. These composite candidates have blended Polish+English embeddings that likely outscore the clean Polish-only title (English food terms like \"GREEN BEANS\" are strongly recognized by the embedding model).\n    30→\n    31→**Secondary cause — structural bonus misallocation:** `\"GREEN BEANS BORKEUM\"` qualifies as `firstStructuralHeading` (ALL_CAPS, 3 words, all ≥4 chars) before bilingual detection runs. It gets `structuralBonus=0.10` + `allCapsBonus=0.08` baked into `scored`. The actual title `\"Smażona zielona fasolka\"` gets zero bonuses. Even after the standalone translation is suppressed, its score dominates the fallback path.\n    32→\n    33→**Fix direction:** Extend bilingual suppression to also remove candidates that *contain* translation text as a contiguous substring (not just as a leading prefix), and avoid assigning structural bonuses to candidates that are subsequently identified as translations.\n    34→============================================================\n    35→# RAW STREAM (5269 events):\n    36→{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"hook_started\",\"hook_id\":\"7da1e755-b454-4cc0-a10c-e36e40869ef1\",\"hook_name\":\"SessionStart:startup\",\"hook_event\":\"SessionStart\",\"uuid\":\"c93aaa4a-0558-4898-8735-5cef7bf2a883\",\"session_id\":\"4ca08c4f-9121-4baa-b94b-0915353a44f7\"}\n    37→{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"hook_response\",\"hook_id\":\"7da1e755-b454-4cc0-a10c-e36e40869ef1\",\"hook_name\":\"SessionStart:startup\",\"hook_event\":\"SessionStart\",\"output\":\"\",\"stdout\":\"\",\"stderr\":\"\",\"exit_code\":0,\"outcome\":\"success\",\"uuid\":\"447ecf79-434c-4f4e-aa67-3860179a3a9f\",\"session_id\":\"4ca08c4f-9121-4baa-b94b-0915353a44f7\"}\n    38→{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"init\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola\",\"session_id\":\"4ca08c4f-9121-4baa-b94b-0915353a44f7\",\"tools\":[\"Task\",\"TaskOutput\",\"Bash\",\"Glob\",\"Grep\",\"ExitPlanMode\",\"Read\",\"Edit\",\"Write\",\"NotebookEdit\",\"WebFetch\",\"TodoWrite\",\"WebSearch\",\"TaskStop\",\"AskUserQuestion\",\"Skill\",\"EnterPlanMode\",\"EnterWorktree\",\"ExitWorktree\",\"CronCreate\",\"CronDelete\",\"CronList\",\"ToolSearch\",\"ListMcpResourcesTool\",\"