ration: 564s — Exit: 0\n# Prompt:\n#   Analyze the title extraction failures below. Read each failing input file\n#   and the current implementation at lib/text-classifier/title-extractor.ts.\n#   \n#   Write your analysis to tools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md explaining:\n#   1. What patterns the algorithm fails on\n#   2. Why each specific failure occurred\n#   3. Common themes across failures\n#   \n#   Do NOT modify any code files. Only write the feedback.md file.\n#   \n#   Failures:\n#   - File: /Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Smażona zielona fasolka.real.txt\n#     Expected: 'Smażona zielona fasolka'\n#     Got: ''\n#   \n#   Results file: tools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/results.txt\n\n============================================================\n\nWritten to `tools/title-loop/docs/16-e59482e/feedback.md`.\n\n## Summary\n\nThe single failure traces to **two interacting bugs** in the trilingual title layout (`Smażona zielona fasolka` / `GREEN BEANS BORKEUM` / `그린빈 볶음`):\n\n**Primary cause — bilingual join contamination:** The bilingual detection correctly removes `\"GREEN BEANS BORKEUM\"` as a standalone candidate, but the filter only suppresses candidates *starting with* the translation text. The 2-line join `\"Smażona zielona fasolka GREEN BEANS BORKEUM\"` and 3-line join including Korean both pass `passesHardFilters` and remain in `scoredForThreshold`. These composite candidates have blended Polish+English embeddings that likely outscore the clean Polish-only title (English food terms like \"GREEN BEANS\" are strongly recognized by the embedding model).\n\n**Secondary cause — structural bonus misallocation:** `\"GREEN BEANS BORKEUM\"` qualifies as `firstStructuralHeading` (ALL_CAPS, 3 words, all ≥4 chars) before bilingual detection runs. It gets `structuralBonus=0.10` + `allCapsBonus=0.08` baked into `scored`. The actual title `\"Smażona zielona fasolka\"` gets zero bonuses. Even after the standalone translation is suppressed, its score dominates the fallback path.\n\n**Fix direction:** Extend bilingual suppression to also remove candidates that *contain* translation text as a contiguous substring (not just as a leading prefix), and avoid assigning structural bonuses to candidates that are subsequently identified as translations.\n============================================================\n# RAW STREAM (5269 events):\n{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"hook_started\",\"hook_id\":\"7da1e755-b454-4cc0-a10c-e36e40869ef1\",\"hook_name\":\"SessionStart:startup\",\"hook_event\":\"SessionStart\",\"uuid\":\"c93aaa4a-0558-4898-8735-5cef7bf2a883\",\"session_id\":\"4ca08c4f-9121-4baa-b94b-0915353a44f7\"}\n{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"hook_response\",\"hook_id\":\"7da1e755-b454-4cc0-a10c-e36e40869ef1\",\"hook_name\":\"SessionStart:startup\",\"hook_event\":\"SessionStart\",\"output\":\"\",\"stdout\":\"\",\"stderr\":\"\",\"exit_code\":0,\"outcome\":\"success\",\"uuid\":\"447ecf79-434c-4f4e-aa67-3860179a3a9f\",\"session_id\":\"4ca08c4f-9121-4baa-b94b-0915353a44f7\"}\n{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"init\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola\",\"session_id\":\"4ca08c4f-9121-4baa-b94b-0915353a44f7\",\"tools\":[\"Task\",\"TaskOutput\",\"Bash\",\"Glob\",\"Grep\",\"ExitPlanMode\",\"Read\",\"Edit\",\"Write\",\"NotebookEdit\",\"WebFetch\",\"TodoWrite\",\"WebSearch\",\"TaskStop\",\"AskUserQuestion\",\"Skill\",\"EnterPlanMode\",\"EnterWorktree\",\"ExitWorktree\",\"CronCreate\",\"CronDelete\",\"CronList\",\"ToolSearch\",\"ListMcpResourcesTool\",\"ReadMcpResourceTool\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Slack__slack_send_message\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Slack__slack_schedule_message\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Slack__slack_create_canvas\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Slack__slack_update_canvas\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Slack__slack_search_public\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Slack__slack_search_public_and_private\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Slack__slack_search_channels\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Slack__slack_search_users\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Slack__slack_read_ch