{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01PRWERsVkhwRpdZuwpHLteN","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete picture. Here's my outline before writing the plan:\n\n**Failure: \"Smażona zielona fasolka\" → empty/undefined**\n\nThree interacting root causes:\n\n1. **Bilingual join contamination** — The bilingual filter removes standalone \"GREEN BEANS BORKEUM\" but the `startsWith` check doesn't catch \"Smażona zielona fasolka GREEN BEANS BORKEUM\" (which starts with Polish). Fix: extend suppression to also remove candidates containing translation text as a suffix or embedded substring.\n\n2. **Structural bonus on translation candidate** — \"GREEN BEANS BORKEUM\" gets structural heading bonus (+0.10) and ALL_CAPS bonus (+0.08) in `scored` before bilingual detection runs. The Polish title gets nothing. Fix: after bilingual detection, if the structural heading was identified as a translation, reassign or nullify the bonus.\n\n3. **Diacritic-stripped section labels** (secondary/non-blocking) — \"SKLADNIKI\" doesn't match \"składniki\" because `isSectionLabel` doesn't normalize diacritics. Fix: strip diacritics via Unicode NFKD before matching."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":448,"cache_read_input_tokens":61558,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":448},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9e805fa1-f282-4af7-9433-5ad139358a2e","uuid":"82b88c2f-df26-48a5-831f-81a3ae032af6"}
